{"tid":2298361,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 南美秘魯烤雞上腿 配 秘魯青醬 拼 煙肉著仔沙律","createTime":"2020-11-24T04:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T09:16:58.000Z","uid":33359,"like":40,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"cc219caacf6a5f8796c226a2a47e2e70b61c80b0","tid":2298361,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/31mWQ50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F31mWQ50.jpg&h=08237fca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1nSpq4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1nSpq4.jpg&h=1fafb894&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rs1jOSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frs1jOSM.jpg&h=f280910f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次呢個醬好似係呢間餐廳第一次出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n專登去試吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞皮燒得岩岩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠香脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肉質都好滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食到有少少檸檬香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個秘魯青醬真係第一次試<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個味唔係好識形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好濃郁得黎又好清新<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落有少少椒香同鹽西香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾特別幾好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n著仔沙律唔洗多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一樣咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落粒黃斑點好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6dccf58f6